Suggested Learning Order (3-Month Roadmap)

Week	Focus
1	Spring Boot Fundamentals
2	JPA + PostgreSQL
3	Product CRUD
4	User Management
5	JWT Security
6	Cart Module
7	Order Module
8	Testing
9	Docker
10	Redis
11	Kafka
12	AWS Deployment

Portfolio Outcome

By the end, you'll have a project demonstrating:

Java 21
Spring Boot 3
PostgreSQL
JPA/Hibernate
JWT Authentication
Spring Security
Redis
Kafka
Docker
AWS
CI/CD
Microservices
System Design

This is the kind of project that can strongly support applications for Backend Engineer/SDE-1 roles and provide talking points for both coding and system design interviews.